  "message": "Show FrankenEye on mobile across 4 subpages\n\nThe floating FrankenEye decorative element was hidden on mobile\nand tablet viewports (hidden lg:block) on 4 page headers.\nChanged to always-visible with responsive positioning and scale:\n\n- Mobile: positioned at top-24 right-4 with smaller scale\n  (1.1x\u20131.4x depending on page)\n- Desktop: original positions restored via md: breakpoint\n  prefixes (top-48, right-[10-15%], scale 1.5x\u20132.2x)\n\nPages affected:\n- architecture: scale-150 \u2192 scale-[1.1] md:scale-150\n- beads: scale-[2.2] \u2192 scale-[1.4] md:scale-[2.2]\n- how-it-was-built: scale-[1.8] \u2192 scale-[1.2] md:scale-[1.8]\n- showcase: scale-[2] \u2192 scale-[1.3] md:scale-[2]\n\nThe eye adds brand personality and visual interest on mobile\nwhere it was previously absent.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
